{"tid":1783140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"fb封韓粉專頁 涉多重賬號篤數","createTime":"2019-12-14T14:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T14:21:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3eeb177a33acadf75f324c4d8b0f26a310811241","tid":1783140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191214/YPZVPRA4JHUTRUDWUUTL7JAZDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191214%2FYPZVPRA4JHUTRUDWUUTL7JAZDI%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=40ae7fb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191214%2FYPZVPRA4JHUTRUDWUUTL7JAZDI%2F&h=f9972690\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191214/YPZVPRA4JHUTRUDWUUTL7JAZDI/</a><br />\n<br />\nfb封韓粉專頁 涉多重賬號篤數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191214/large/1576252624_970a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576252624_970a.gif&h=f46f1f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣網民昨日發現無法進入部份總統參選人的facebook後援會相關社團，其中包括社團成員超過15萬人的「2020韓國瑜總統後援會（總會）」。fb接受傳媒查詢時回應稱，昨日在台灣移除118個粉絲專頁、99個社團及51個多重賬號，原因是違反社群守則。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓副手諷蔡沒生小孩<br />\n<br />\n據中央社報道，fb昨回應該社查詢時表示，對任何違反社群守則，包含冒充身份與不實的互動手法，一向會採取行動。而昨日，fb在台灣移除了118個粉絲專頁、99個社團，以及用來管理這些粉絲專頁與社團的51個多重賬號。這51個多重賬號試圖以虛假手法提高貼文內容的人氣，違反fb的社群守則。fb強調，隨着台灣選舉即將到來，將持續偵測平台上不實的互動手法以及其餘違反社群守則的行為，並主動採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n此外，國民黨副總統候選人張善政前日舉辦新住民座談時，稱總統蔡英文「沒生過小孩，不知道父母的心」，遭外界批是歧視女性。蔡英文也特別在fb發文還擊：「未婚沒孩子一樣可以照顧好台灣囝仔。」張善政昨回應時，先將前日原話重複說三遍，強調原意是關心懷孕新住民媽媽的健保權利，並喊冤遭斷章取義。但有記者指他的原話聽起來還是像歧視，張善政最後改口說，那他收回這段話，改成向蔡英文喊話、請蔡給新住民媽媽健保權利。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"ca9d7f4a5e50e7c52c3063e69f47a81487a1388f","tid":1783140,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:18:59.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6568656301137cfb57c771412871de90d978b333","tid":1783140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDHdKiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDHdKiw.jpg&h=779c8437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCCpQSW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCCpQSW.jpg&h=7105947f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}